After working on it the whole day (since 12pm AZ time), I have finally fully 
updated the site with every char sheet that I got. The Character page should 
be easier to understand now.

The Maximals at the Ark and at the CF are one faction, Minime.

::Ramulus::

Ramulus nods, walking back toward the pod.

"Allright," he says, looking at it. He had delt with pods before, and he 
figured he could deal with this one, "Whenever you're ready."

Ramulus stands at the pod, ready to activate the scanners.
